HEADWORD: Ronchil
<hw>Ron"chil</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Sp.
<ets>ronquillo</ets> slightly hoarse.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
